data.description: Charming David Weekley Craftsman in The Falls offering a 25yd Lap Pool with Sun Deck, Hot Tub, and Pool Bath! Features a versatile layout with over 4,000sqft and tons of storage! The primary home offers 4 Bedrooms (3 down, 1 up) each with en suite bath & large closets, study, formal dining, and huge gameroom! A private Garage Apartment offers investment potential or the perfect retreat as the 5th Bedroom with full bath. Enjoy entertaining with an outdoor kitchen & outdoor fireplace with No Rear Neighbors, as this Oversized lot backs to a Greenbelt in the Gated section of Sable Park! Garage enthusiasts will be impressed with this supersized 3-Car garage with a 200V for electric vehicles. Exterior freshly painted in 2022! Residents in the Falls enjoy top-rated CISD schools, easy access to Grand Parkway, IAH, The Woodlands, I-45, Hardy Toll Road, and Major Medical. Plus the 100-acre Lake Holcomb, Clubhouse with gym, playgrounds, parks, trails, pools, splashpad, dog park, and YMCA complex.
